---
// MethodologySection - The Furum Methodology with stats and process steps
---

<section class="methodology-section" id="process">
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>The Furum Methodology</h2>
      <p>A holistic approach to gym growth that focuses on the metrics that actually impact your bank account.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats Grid -->
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-value">+52%</div>
        <p class="stat-label">Avg Member Growth</p>
        <p class="stat-desc">We don't just find people; we find the <strong>right</strong> people who value your premium service.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-card featured">
        <div class="stat-value">4.2x</div>
        <p class="stat-label">ROAS Guarantee</p>
        <p class="stat-desc">If we don't hit our agreed targets within 90 days, we work for free until we do. Total accountability.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-value">-30%</div>
        <p class="stat-label">Churn Reduction</p>
        <p class="stat-desc">Automated onboarding and engagement sequences that keep your members loyal and paying.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Process Steps -->
    <div class="process-grid">
      <div class="process-step">
        <span class="step-number">Step 01</span>
        <h4>The Audit</h4>
        <p>We analyze your current funnel, cost per acquisition, and LTV to find the leak.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process-step">
        <span class="step-number">Step 02</span>
        <h4>High-Ticket Funnel</h4>
        <p>Building a custom landing page and ad creative designed for premium conversions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process-step">
        <span class="step-number">Step 03</span>
        <h4>Sales Enablement</h4>
        <p>We train your staff on our proprietary 'Consultation-to-Contract' closing script.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process-step">
        <span class="step-number">Step 04</span>
        <h4>Scale & Automate</h4>
        <p>As the cash flows in, we optimize the systems so you spend less time in the weeds.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Background accent -->
  <div class="bg-accent"></div>
</section>

<style>
  .methodology-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: hsl(var(--forest));
    color: white;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .methodology-section {
      padding: 8rem 0;
    }
  }

  .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Header */
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto 5rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: hsl(var(--cream) / 0.7);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Stats Grid */
  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .stats-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }

  .stat-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    background: hsl(var(--cream) / 0.03);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid hsl(var(--cream) / 0.1);
    border-radius: 1rem;
  }

  .stat-card.featured {
    background: hsl(var(--cream) / 0.05);
    border-color: hsl(var(--cream) / 0.2);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .stat-card.featured {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: hsl(var(--gold));
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    font-weight: 700;
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .stat-desc {
    color: hsl(var(--cream) / 0.8);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .stat-desc strong {
    color: white;
  }

  /* Process Grid */
  .process-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .process-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .process-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .process-step {
    padding-left: 2rem;
    border-left: 2px solid hsl(var(--cream) / 0.1);
  }

  .step-number {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: hsl(var(--gold));
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .process-step h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .process-step p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: hsl(var(--cream) / 0.6);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Background accent */
  .bg-accent {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 33%;
    height: 100%;
    background: hsl(var(--cream) / 0.05);
    transform: skewX(-12deg) translateX(5rem);
    transform-origin: top;
    z-index: 0;
  }
</style>
